    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Craniella quirimure sp. nov. A. Two specimens alive in an aquarium. Scale bar 2 cm. B. Specimen sectioned sagitally to show inner color pattern. Scale bar 2 cm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/169742/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169743>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4 Schematic representation of the megasclere complement and SEM of the microscleres of the holotype. A. Protriaene I. B. Cladome of the prodiaene I. C. Protriaene II. D. Cladome of the prodiaene II. E. Oxea I (main, choanosomal). F. Oxea II (cortical). G. Oxea III (anisoxea, choanosomal). H. Oxea IV (rhizoidal). I. Anatriaene. J. Sigmaspire. Scale bar in m: A­D, I = 25; E = 250; F­H = 100 and J = 2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/169743/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

